 <lb n="1"/>fa ʾin nī ʾaḥmadu ăl lāha ăllaḏī lā 
 <lb n="2"/>ʾilāha ʾillā huwa 
 <lb n="3"/>ʾammā baʿdu fa ʾiḏā ǧāʾa ka 
 <lb n="4"/>kitāb ī hāḏā fa ŭnẓuri ăl qumuṣa 
 <lb n="5"/>ăllatī ʿalà ʾarḍi ka fa ʿaǧǧil 
 <lb n="6"/>bi hā ʾilay ya wa ḥīna tanẓur fī 
 <lb n="7"/>ăl qumuṣi fa lā tuʾaḫḫiranna min hā 
 <lb n="8"/>šayʾ:an fa ʾin nī ʾurīdu ʾan 
 <lb n="9"/>ʾursila bi hā ʾilà ʾamīri 
 <lb n="10"/>ăl muʾminīna ʾin šāʾa ăl lāhu 
 <lb n="11"/>wa ĭʿlam ʾan nī la ʾin ʾaḫḫarta 
 <lb n="12"/>min hā šayʾ:an la yuṣībanna ka minn ī 
 <lb n="13"/>mā yaḍurru yuḥzinu ka fī nafsi ka 
 <lb n="14"/>wa māli ʿāʾilati ka wa taʿahhad ĭbḏil li tuwaffiqa tuwaffiya nī mā 
 <lb n="15"/>ʾamartu ka bi hi qabla ăl ʾaḍḥà 
 <lb n="16"/>baʿda ăl yawmi bi ṯalāṯīna wa ăs salāmu 
 <lb n="17"/>ʿalà mani ĭttabaʿa ăl hudà 
 <lb n="18"/>wa kataba ḫubayšu bnu ʿadiyy:in 
 <lb n="19"/>fī ḏī ăl qaʿdaẗi min sanaẗi 
 <lb n="20"/>tisʿīna 
